{"tid":762622,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"關於ban煩膠","createTime":"2018-07-31T12:26:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T14:04:15.000Z","uid":147721,"like":26,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"f549708de8dd762b836757a97745a52841aeb794","tid":762622,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T12:26:18.000Z","msg":"建議唔好永久ban煩膠<br />\n而係開一個煩膠台 比佢地淨係可以係個台入面回覆<br />\n畢竟有啲會員本身都係某啲圈子到傾開<br />\n永久ban佢地 係懲罰埋其他同佢地傾開計既無辜會員<br />\n例子 ban如浮雲未知曉同可愛 係懲罰左其他係感情台同佢地傾開計既會員<br />\n<br />\n同埋想問連囝 肥絲咁都唔算洗版？咁又唔ban肥絲？<br />\n你都推出左永久封鎖功能比會員自己揀ban邊個<br />\n咁你又係論壇管理層面ban人<br />\n咁係論壇管理層面ban人既準則係咩<br />\n點解肥絲大隻唔係論壇層面永久ban"},{"pid":"d37eb994aa3b5f06c41e9b1ec9966652eabc3e82","tid":762622,"uid":93655,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T12:43:03.000Z","msg":"啱呀"},{"pid":"f6aeb5b9475a6742d3c2ec329ea5586eeb18e6fc","tid":762622,"uid":148185,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T12:46:50.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"3849d421f24bb26a07d65c16c696827aa1724ffa","tid":762622,"uid":8572,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T12:56:45.000Z","msg":"原來浮雲狗比人ban 左 我完全封鎖左佢好耐  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點都好 我絕對支持admin決定 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n記得唔好封鎖me <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c7bb7de8a4bbebdd6a80173707b8ab7a1a2bc48","tid":762622,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T12:58:30.000Z","msg":"咁都ban 傻撚左？"},{"pid":"db022ab7a51d9119dcf7dbcf7418996d8435206b","tid":762622,"uid":10759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T12:59:12.000Z","msg":"係咪要清算哂成個感動台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d42d0d03c8f2ec5e39d28c23cc107054753eecf","tid":762622,"uid":11598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T